SET TALK OFF

* ============================================================
* X64_MEMO_GROWTH_STAGE2.DTS
*
* Purpose:
*   Push X64 memo growth farther using repeated appends on the
*   current public DotTalk++ command surface.
*
* Scope:
*   - CREATE X64
*   - scalar field writes
*   - repeated memo self-append
*   - close/reopen persistence
*   - clear/reinsert cycle
*
* Notes:
*   - Uses X64 xBase memo storage (.dtx backend), not VFP.
*   - Avoids LOCAL / DO WHILE / unsupported FoxPro syntax.
*   - Repeated literal chunk appends are used as a practical
*     stand-in for procedural large-memo generation.
* ============================================================

CLOSE ALL
SCHEMAS CLOSE

ERASE MEMO_SIZE_X64 CONFIRM

* ---------- 1. CREATE ----------
CREATE X64 MEMO_SIZE_X64 ( ;
    ID       N(8,0), ;
    TITLE    C(40), ;
    NOTES    M )


USE MEMO_SIZE_X64

* ---------- 2. APPEND BASE RECORD ----------
APPEND
REPLACE ID    WITH 1
REPLACE TITLE WITH "X64 MEMO SIZE TEST"
REPLACE NOTES WITH "BEGIN X64 MEMO SIZE TEST."

DISPLAY
STRUCT
FIELDS
TUPLE *

* ---------- 3. SMALL BASELINE APPENDS ----------
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0001] The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0002] This memo is being grown through repeated appends."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0003] DotTalk++ X64 memo path baseline."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0004] Persistence check follows."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0005] End of small baseline block."

DISPLAY
TUPLE *

CLOSE
USE MEMO_SIZE_X64
DISPLAY
TUPLE *

* ---------- 4. MEDIUM GROWTH BLOCK A ----------
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0101] Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0102] Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0103] Duis aute irure dolor in reprehenderit in voluptate velit esse cillum dolore eu fugiat nulla pariatur."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0104] Excepteur sint occaecat cupidatat non proident, sunt in culpa qui officia deserunt mollit anim id est laborum."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0105] Repeating prose is acceptable here because the purpose is storage growth rather than semantic richness."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0106] The memo should preserve all prior content after every append."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0107] If the memo engine breaks, corruption or truncation may appear after reopen."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0108] This block is intentionally moderate in size."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0109] The current shell lacks procedural loops, so explicit lines are used."
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0110] End of medium growth block A."

CLOSE
USE MEMO_SIZE_X64
DISPLAY
TUPLE *

* ---------- 5. MEDIUM GROWTH BLOCK B ----------
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0201] ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz 0123456789"
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0202] ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz 0123456789"
REPLACE NOTES WITH NOTES + " [0203] ABCDEFGHIJKLMNOPQRSTUVWXYZ abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz 0123456789"
